    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, minor door dings, and some fading on the clear coat in certain areas. Inside, the upholstery shows visible wear and some staining from regular use, but all essential electronics and climate controls are functioning. It runs and drives well for its age, making it a solid choice for someone prioritizing utility over aesthetics.",
